					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616#post-4766886</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616/remember#post-4766886</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 04 Sep 2020 14:49:58 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>BANANASUNITED</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6494835</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Just one question: why 10,653 years? According to the source of the original story, the Earth is 5780 years old, and the Cain and Able story most likely occurred between 80 and 120 years after creation. It's just a nitpick, and if this isn't meant to be directly based on the source, then it's completely fine, but it's just something for you to consider.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
