				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616#post-4366079</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616/remember#post-4366079</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2019 20:14:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Cerastes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3352053</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>As much as I agree that some of the series 1 skips can be a bit overused, the biblical ones are some of my favourite ones on the site and I'm a huge sucker for stories involving them. Lilith I feel is painfully underused, and I plan on writing about her a lot more.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
