						 <p>Thanks! Yeah I added the part with Lilith after some people suggested it was a little too short. This tale is a bit of a spiritual 2.0 to another draft of mine, which had Lilith and Cain meeting during a containment breach. I decided not to go with that one, and instead fold Lilith into this one.</p> 
