					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616#post-4365637</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616/remember#post-4365637</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2019 13:05:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>WindyCat</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3358922</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm not sure if you added the bit with Lilith after I read this as a draft or if I somehow skipped over it while I gave my quick crit, but I super like it! I forgot to say this while critting, but I also like the bit with 3000. It never crossed my mind that Cain would try seeking it out, but it makes so much sense.</p> <p>Overall, I still like this tale. I'm glad that someone detailed how big of a toll not being able to forget his biggest mistake and everything after that would have on Cain. These small character study pieces are what I live for.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616#post-4365188</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12545616/remember#post-4365188</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2019 04:20:52 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Cerastes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3352053</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The worst thing about living forever with a perfect memory is that no matter what, you'll always remember your worst day as if it happened yesterday.</p> <p>Thank you to WindyCat, DrChandra, Dylsexion, Bardbarb, and DrAkimoto on the IRC channels for taking the time to review my drafts and giving me feed back.</p> <p>Also wanted to specially thank the following people for inspiring parts of the story:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=213153&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="DrClef" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=213153)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" >DrClef</a></span> for making his 001 proposal, the Gate Guardian.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kondraki" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2785959&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="Kondraki" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2785959)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kondraki" >Kondraki</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/communism-will-win" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=617958&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="Communism will win" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=617958)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/communism-will-win" >Communism will win</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lumancer" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=662776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="Lumancer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=662776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lumancer" >Lumancer</a></span> for writing SCP-336, AKA Lilit Bat Asherah.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/joreth" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1370009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="Joreth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1370009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/joreth" >Joreth</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" >djkaktus</a></span> for writing SCP-3000.</li> <li>While I'm here, shout out to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span> again for letting me use their SCP-4818 in my tale.</li> <li>And another big thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1568664501" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" >djkaktus</a></span> again for SCP-4840, which is one of the few mentions of Lilith outside of the 239 tale, and also expertly weaves SCP-3000 in the greater quasi-biblical canon.</li> </ul> 
				 	]]>
